Package: wickraxray
Type: Package
Title: Data-Driven Market-Microstructure Frame Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-xray over its C ABI hub: build an Xray from a
    spec JSON, drive it with command JSON and read back render frames - the same
    protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-xray
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-xray/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-xray C ABI shared library (WKXRAY_LIB) and its
    header (WKXRAY_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
